metadata.name: Estate
metadata.description:
LA DOLCE VITA is a collection of analogue photographs from Italy, taken during the summer of 2021. This collection aims to take a new look at the timeless beauty of everyday things that surround us, such as colors, shapes or lights. "Estate" means summer in italian.
This image was taken in: Genova Italy.
